    "description": "<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >这是一款手感复古的动作街机游戏。</h2></strong><br>通过操作三个身份不同的主角，不断击败追杀而来的刺客，解开谜团和拯救城市。并从三个主角不同的剧情，拼凑出整个故事的全貌。<br>灵感来自于“Captain Commando&quot;和“Cadillacs and Dinosaurs”。我们学习并借鉴了其中的部分机制，让Fury Fight中的战斗尽可能的还原90年代街机的操作感，希望唤醒当年街机给玩家所带来的快乐。并且，我们仿制了“Captain Commando&quot;中的经典关卡，以致敬那个辉煌的街机年代。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496150/extras/f3b972ad4ec5bfb21532781823b370ef.webp?t=1652150144\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496150/extras/f3b972ad4ec5bfb21532781823b370ef.poster.avif?t=1652150144\" class=\"bb_img\" width=640 height=27 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>畅爽街机体验，真正清版打斗</strong></h2>致敬令人怀念的经典时代，来一段简单直接的快乐体验吧！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496150/extras/7fd8a56f44faa3c241df5bcabbc879f1.poster.avif?t=1652150144\" width=640 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496150/extras/7fd8a56f44faa3c241df5bcabbc879f1.webm?t=1652150144\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496150/extras/7fd8a56f44faa3c241df5bcabbc879f1.mp4?t=1652150144\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>紧张刺激的Boss对决，电光火石的招式比拼</strong></h2>每个Boss都有鲜明的特点（槽点？），更有强力非常的绝技，莽or苟？来一些极限点的操作吧！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496150/extras/13c81a81072b7fbf8156e9d88b015b13.poster.avif?t=1652150144\" width=640 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496150/extras/13c81a81072b7fbf8156e9d88b015b13.webm?t=1652150144\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496150/extras/13c81a81072b7fbf8156e9d88b015b13.mp4?t=1652150144\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>双人合作闯关，兄弟，我的背后交给你了！</strong></h2>还记得在街机厅里和兄弟共同打机的欢乐吗？这里就来了，帮队友解围，还是抢队友的血？<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496150/extras/4e6c276d7dbe4b392c9692f826e04cab.poster.avif?t=1652150144\" width=640 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496150/extras/4e6c276d7dbe4b392c9692f826e04cab.webm?t=1652150144\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496150/extras/4e6c276d7dbe4b392c9692f826e04cab.mp4?t=1652150144\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>有多种难度可以供选择</strong></h2>可以在关卡中与敌人触发对话，探索不同的支线剧情。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496150/extras/a537aed057cbaab5c31ae5166b989a6c.poster.avif?t=1652150144\" width=640 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496150/extras/a537aed057cbaab5c31ae5166b989a6c.webm?t=1652150144\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496150/extras/a537aed057cbaab5c31ae5166b989a6c.mp4?t=1652150144\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>一个可供解锁的游戏画廊</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496150/extras/ed12027c9240f238c56df6fe93d580eb.poster.avif?t=1652150144\" width=640 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496150/extras/ed12027c9240f238c56df6fe93d580eb.webm?t=1652150144\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496150/extras/ed12027c9240f238c56df6fe93d580eb.mp4?t=1652150144\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496150/extras/fb395d5ff29f1b8f233b9cb769416c96.webp?t=1652150144\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496150/extras/fb395d5ff29f1b8f233b9cb769416c96.poster.avif?t=1652150144\" class=\"bb_img\" width=640 height=27 /></picture></span><br><br>无边的宇宙，无尽的冲突<br><br>这是一个关于寻找的故事，穷其一生，不计代价；<br>这是一个关于守护的故事，跨越时空，遍体鳞伤；<br>这是一个关于正义的故事，热血少年，勇往直前；<br>这还是一个爱与恶，罪与罚，灵与肉之间，碰撞交错的故事。<br>三位英雄在奇异的命运中聚首，惊天阴谋之下，不测宿命之中，他们能否拨开迷雾，逃出生天？<br>高悬天宇的虚空星球，光怪陆离的繁华都市，阴暗地道中嗜血的怪笑声，神秘基地中美艳的女博士，朝阳下飞来海上的荒漠......逝者如川，一切尚未开端，一切已然结束。<br>而那个人，踏遍万千宇宙，穷尽碧落虚空，所思所求将要触手可及之时，命运，又将给出怎样的答案？<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496150/extras/2fc03f4faa8c890cde699278206b23c2.webp?t=1652150144\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496150/extras/2fc03f4faa8c890cde699278206b23c2.poster.avif?t=1652150144\" class=\"bb_img\" width=640 height=27 /></picture></span><br><strong>霍凯</strong><br>怒发卷残云，神拳碎钛金<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496150/extras/f919d5117c0c4eeb2638df3dee8ba2b4.poster.avif?t=1652150144\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496150/extras/f919d5117c0c4eeb2638df3dee8ba2b4.webm?t=1652150144\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>霍凯是一位富有正义感的警长，同时也是强大的印第安战士。为了找到失踪的姐姐，他循着线索来到这座城市。他的攻击充满力量，拥有多种强力的投技。他的格挡因为特殊血统的能力，能无效化敌人的大部分攻击。<br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</h2></strong><br><strong>阿拉德</strong><br>闪转破瞬刹，飒沓越流星。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496150/extras/9c571a437d41d40b1fd822bfb0eab0d4.poster.avif?t=1652150144\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496150/extras/9c571a437d41d40b1fd822bfb0eab0d4.webm?t=1652150144\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>阿拉德是学校的运动明星，单纯而又热血。刚转校不久，便因为太显眼，被校篮球队队长约战单挑，从而被卷入事件。过人的运动能力使得他非常灵活，闪避和二段跳让他可以游走在敌人之间。他还可以使用炫酷的球技眩晕周围的敌人。<br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</h2></strong><br><strong>红羊</strong><br>疾风追魅影，爆裂驱邪光<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496150/extras/bbf28c9a8b9c0ebab56787e168d8e182.poster.avif?t=1652150144\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496150/extras/bbf28c9a8b9c0ebab56787e168d8e182.webm?t=1652150144\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>红羊并不是她的真名，只是一个代号。她的身份和过去都是谜团。她可能是一个特工，但没人知道她的目标。她拥有高超的战斗技巧，可以使出复杂的攻击动作。通过启动超频，她能在短时间内获得超越极限的可怕力量。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496150/extras/0c3d4836157049e8451b943d8a124c09.webp?t=1652150144\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496150/extras/0c3d4836157049e8451b943d8a124c09.poster.avif?t=1652150144\" class=\"bb_img\" width=640 height=27 /></picture></span><br>我们很清楚，现阶段Fury Fight的视觉表现十分的粗糙，这也是我们迟迟没有推出游戏的原因。但在热心玩家们的鼓励下，我们最终决定推出此游戏。为此，我们会定一个低廉并合理的价格，让每个购买的玩家都物有所值。并且我们以爷爷的名字承诺，会将所有收入全部投入进对游戏的改进与新内容的开发中。请大家拭目以待。<br><br>热爱经典游戏，但我们并不是老古董；<br><br>热衷开发游戏，但我们并不沽名钓誉；<br><br>我们人数不多，资金更是有限，但这些都不影响我们的认真，执着，谦虚！<br><br>感谢你们看到这个页面，我们诚挚的期待任何你们的意见，渴望听到大家奇妙的想法，请在steam私信我们，或者加入官方玩家QQ群.<br>QQ群号:604384699。<br><br>我们的理想就是：做大家想要的游戏！",
